<section class="section"><div class="wrap"><div class="section-head"><p class="eyebrow">How it works</p><h2>From idea to launch—in four clear phases.</h2><p>Early decisions on partners, venues and programme keep the whole Week moving forward.</p></div><div class="timeline"><article class="step"><div class="node"></div><p class="eyebrow">Months 1–2</p><h3>Foundations</h3><p>Partners, venues and programme direction are confirmed.</p></article><article class="step"><div class="node"></div><p class="eyebrow">Months 3–4</p><h3>Outreach</h3><p>Speakers, sponsors, schools and contributors are brought in.</p></article><article class="step"><div class="node"></div><p class="eyebrow">Months 5–6</p><h3>Launch</h3><p>Registration, publicity and the media plan go live.</p></article><article class="step"><div class="node"></div><p class="eyebrow">Event week</p><h3>Delivery</h3><p>Citywide events run, followed by impact reporting.</p></article></div></div></section>
